<section class="about-me section" id="about-me">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title fade-in-up">Conoce a tu Contador de Confianza</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle fade-in-up">
          Más de 10 años ayudando a empresarios mexicanos a crecer sin
          preocuparse por temas fiscales
        </p>
      </div>
    <div class="about-content fade-in-up">
      <div class="about-image">
        <div class="image-placeholder">
            <img src="/images/photo.png" alt="Israel Castro Urieta - Contador Especialista" class="profile-image">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-text">
        <div class="about-description">
          <p class="about-lead">
            <strong>Especialista en Contabilidad Fiscal</strong> con amplia experiencia en automatización de procesos contables para
            PyMEs mexicanas.
          </p>

          <p>
            He ayudado a más de 150 empresarios a optimizar su carga fiscal y
            automatizar sus procesos contables, permitiéndoles enfocar su
            energía en hacer crecer sus negocios mientras yo me encargo de
            mantener todo en orden con el SAT.
          </p>

          <p>
            Mi filosofía es simple: <em
              >"La contabilidad debe ser tu aliada, no tu dolor de cabeza"</em
            >. Por eso desarrollo soluciones tecnológicas que simplifican lo
            complejo y garantizan el cumplimiento fiscal sin complicaciones.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-me {
    background: var(--color-white);
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-me::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent,
      var(--color-border),
      transparent
    );
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Image Section */
  .about-image {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .image-placeholder {
    width: 280px;
    height: 350px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--color-background) 0%,
      var(--color-background-alt) 100%
    );
    border: 2px dashed var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .image-placeholder::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -2px;
    left: -2px;
    right: -2px;
    bottom: -2px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--color-primary),
      var(--color-success)
    );
    border-radius: 16px;
    z-index: -1;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .image-placeholder:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .image-placeholder:hover::before {
    opacity: 0.1;
  }

  .placeholder-icon {
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .image-placeholder:hover .placeholder-icon {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .placeholder-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .image-placeholder:hover .placeholder-text {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  /* Text Content */
  .about-text .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .about-text .section-title {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .about-text .section-subtitle {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .about-description {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .about-description p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .about-lead {
    font-size: 1.1rem !important;
    color: var(--color-text-primary) !important;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 2rem !important;
  }

  .about-lead strong {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-description em {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-text .section-header {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-content {
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .image-placeholder {
      width: 240px;
      height: 300px;
    }

    .placeholder-icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    .about-text .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .image-placeholder {
      width: 200px;
      height: 250px;
    }

    .placeholder-icon {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .placeholder-text {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }

  /* Alternative: When you add a real image, use this class */
  .about-image img,
  .about-image .profile-image {
    width: 280px;
    height: 350px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.15);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .about-image img:hover,
  .about-image .profile-image:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.2);
  }
</style>
